          <h2 class="font-mono text-cyan text-[13px] uppercase tracking-[0.15em] mb-4">2. Informational Purpose</h2>
          <p>
            This website is provided for general informational purposes only. It is not transactional — no goods or services can be purchased through this site. The content is intended to outline DigiSite's business concept and attract potential partners, advertisers, and investors.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- 3. Financial Projections Disclaimer -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-mono text-cyan text-[13px] uppercase tracking-[0.15em] mb-4">3. Financial Projections Disclaimer</h2>
          <p>
            This website contains <strong class="text-off-white">forward-looking statements</strong>, including but not limited to projected revenue figures, income estimates, and financial projections (such as projected annual revenue per screen, combined revenue scenarios, and revenue-sharing models). These figures are estimates based on internal assumptions and are provided for illustrative purposes only.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            Forward-looking statements are inherently uncertain and actual results may differ materially from those projected. They should not be relied upon as a guarantee or promise of future performance. DigiSite Limited makes no representation or warranty as to the accuracy, completeness, or achievability of any projected figures.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            Nothing on this website constitutes financial advice, investment advice, or a solicitation to invest. You should seek independent professional advice before making any financial decisions based on information presented here.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- 4. Market Data Disclaimer -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-mono text-cyan text-[13px] uppercase tracking-[0.15em] mb-4">4. Market Data Disclaimer</h2>
          <p>
            This website references third-party market data and industry statistics, including figures relating to the Digital Out-of-Home (DOOH) advertising market. While we endeavour to use reliable and up-to-date sources, DigiSite Limited does not warrant the accuracy or completeness of any third-party data presented on this site.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            Market data is provided for context and illustration only and should not be relied upon for investment or business decisions without independent verification.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- 5. Intellectual Property -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-mono text-cyan text-[13px] uppercase tracking-[0.15em] mb-4">5. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>
            All content on this website — including text, graphics, logos, images, design elements, and code — is the property of DigiSite Limited or its licensors and is protected by copyright and intellectual property laws.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            You may not reproduce, distribute, modify, or create derivative works from any content on this website without our prior written consent.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- 6. No Warranties -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-mono text-cyan text-[13px] uppercase tracking-[0.15em] mb-4">6. No Warranties</h2>
          <p>
            This website is provided on an <strong class="text-off-white">"as is" and "as available"</strong> basis. DigiSite Limited makes no warranties or representations, express or implied, regarding the operation of the site, the accuracy of its content, or its suitability for any particular purpose.
