          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- 7. Limitation of Liability -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-mono text-cyan text-[13px] uppercase tracking-[0.15em] mb-4">7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>
            To the fullest extent permitted by applicable law, DigiSite Limited shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, or special damages arising out of or in connection with your use of this website or reliance on any information provided herein.
